                            <div class="border-start border-danger border-3 ps-3 mb-3">
                                <ul class="small">
                                    <li><strong>Phishing:</strong> Fraudulent emails to steal credentials</li>
                                    <li><strong>Spear Phishing:</strong> Targeted phishing attacks</li>
                                    <li><strong>Whaling:</strong> Phishing targeting executives</li>
                                    <li><strong>Business Email Compromise (BEC):</strong> CEO fraud</li>
                                    <li><strong>Email Spoofing:</strong> Forging sender addresses</li>
                                    <li><strong>Malware Attachments:</strong> Infected files</li>
                                    <li><strong>Spam:</strong> Unsolicited bulk email</li>
